---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Case Study: How Nguyen Construction Increased Win Rate to 43% | Lead Flow North">
  <article class="py-12 md:py-20">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6">
      <!-- Back Link -->
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto mb-8">
        <a href="/industries/home-services/general-contractors" class="inline-flex items-center text-sky-600 hover:text-sky-700 font-medium">
          <svg class="w-4 h-4 mr-2" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M15 19l-7-7 7-7"></path></svg>
          Back to General Contractor Services
        </a>
      </div>
      
      <header class="max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center mb-12">
        <div class="flex items-center justify-center gap-4 mb-6">
          <span class="bg-green-100 text-green-700 px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-sm font-medium">Case Study</span>
          <span class="text-slate-500 text-sm">5 min read</span>
        </div>
        <h1 class="text-3xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-6">
          How Nguyen Construction Increased Win Rate to 43%
        </h1>
        <p class="text-xl text-slate-600 mb-8">
          A Surrey general contractor transformed bid follow-up and client communication.
        </p>
      </header>

      <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto mb-12">
        <div class="bg-gradient-to-r from-stone-600 to-amber-600 rounded-2xl p-8 md:p-12 text-white">
          <div class="grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-4 gap-8">
            <div class="text-center">
              <div class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold mb-2">43%</div>
              <div class="text-stone-100">Bid Win Rate</div>
            </div>
            <div class="text-center">
              <div class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold mb-2">67%</div>
              <div class="text-stone-100">'Exceptional' Rating</div>
            </div>
            <div class="text-center">
              <div class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold mb-2">4.1x</div>
              <div class="text-stone-100">Referral Increase</div>
            </div>
            <div class="text-center">
              <div class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold mb-2">$89K</div>
              <div class="text-stone-100">Avg Project Value</div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto">
        <div class="prose prose-lg prose-slate max-w-none">

          <div class="bg-slate-100 p-6 rounded-xl my-8 not-prose">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-slate-900 mb-4">Client Overview</h3>
            <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-4 text-sm">
              <div>
                <span class="text-slate-600">Business:</span>
                <span class="font-medium text-slate-900 ml-2">Nguyen Construction</span>
              </div>
              <div>
                <span class="text-slate-600">Location:</span>
                <span class="font-medium text-slate-900 ml-2">Surrey, BC</span>
              </div>
              <div>
                <span class="text-slate-600">Type:</span>
                <span class="font-medium text-slate-900 ml-2">Residential general contractor</span>
              </div>
              <div>
                <span class="text-slate-600">Services:</span>
                <span class="font-medium text-slate-900 ml-2">Renovations, additions, custom builds</span>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 mt-12 mb-4">The Challenge</h2>

          <p>
            Tom Nguyen had skilled crews but inconsistent projects. Bids were submitted but rarely followed up. Clients felt ignored mid-project. Reviews were sparse. Referrals happened randomly.
          </p>

          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 mt-12 mb-4">The Solution</h2>

          <p>We implemented automated bid follow-up sequences, milestone-based project updates with photo sharing, systematic review requests at project completion, and structured referral campaigns with incentives.</p>

          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 mt-12 mb-4">The Results</h2>

          <p>Bid win rate jumped to 43%. Client satisfaction surveys showed 67% rating projects as 'exceptional.' Referrals increased 4.1x. Average project value rose to $89K.</p>

          <blockquote class="border-l-4 border-stone-500 pl-6 my-8">
            <p class="text-xl text-slate-700 italic mb-4">
              "The bid follow-up was the biggest change. We used to submit and forget. Now we stay in touch for weeks and win business we would have lost."
            </p>
            <cite class="text-slate-600 not-italic">â€” Tom Nguyen, Owner</cite>
          </blockquote>

          <div class="bg-gradient-to-r from-stone-600 to-amber-600 p-8 rounded-xl text-white my-12">
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4 text-white">Ready to Win More Projects?</h3>
            <a href="/contact" class="inline-flex items-center bg-white text-stone-600 px-6 py-3 rounded-lg font-semibold hover:bg-slate-100 transition">
              Book Your Free Demo
            </a>
          </div>

        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </article>
</Layout>
